{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "維護榮耀", "storyInfo": "年幼的王嗣帶著諸王之息出現在眾人面前，歡呼聲下暗流湧動，倫蒂尼姆風雨欲來。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......阿勒黛，偷聽可不是什麼好習慣。聽父親的話。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有卑鄙小人才會躲在暗處謀劃別人的生死。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們也許能以此牟利，但這種竊來的勝利必不會長久。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唔......他們都是卑鄙小人......）", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（爸爸......）", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不想被抓個正著，尤其是被這些壞人抓住。這會讓父親失望，也會令坎伯蘭之名蒙羞。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是她能爬到窗戶外面去的話......"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們得抓緊時間下去。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵們正在清點人數。我們趁亂混進人群裡，這樣的話，沒有人能發現我們曾經離開過。", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你聽見什麼聲音了嗎？", "name": "看不清臉的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.7, "name2": "avg_npc_177", "blackstart2": 0.2, "blackend2": 0.7, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不定是什麼小動物。別多想了，這麼窄的屋子怎麼藏人？", "name": "面目模糊的軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她小心翼翼地蜷縮在陰影裡。最忠誠的盟友——巨大的蒸汽甲胄替她打著掩護。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的手指觸摸到了窗戶的邊緣，只要能翻窗出去，她就能躲開這兩個人的視線，沿著水管爬下去。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裙子已經髒了，艾爾希一定會不高興的。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但只要能不被抓住......"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 200.0, "g": 200.0, "b": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "imagerotate", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 啊！", "name": "阿勒黛"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "xScaleTo": 1.3, "yScaleTo": 1.3, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "imagerotate", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不明白發生了什麼。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是天地都跟著在她眼前旋轉起來，阿勒黛的腦袋暈暈的，手腳都沒了力氣，該抓住的該踩住的都落了空，直直地從二樓跌了下來。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花園的景色正在瘋狂地砸向她的腦袋，可在她摔到堅硬的泥地上之前，一塊又軟又厚的墊子輕輕托住了她。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "imagerotate", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪來的墊子？"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是墊子。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛感覺自己被溫柔地放在了地上。"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她回過頭去，看向身後——"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "block": "true", "image": "blocker_movi", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i01_1", "fadetime": 1.0, "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只應存在於傳說中的生物正站在她的面前。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_deeplion", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "slide", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "soundvolume", "attributes": {"channel": "slide", "volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們彷彿剛從神話中走來，威風凜凜地站在花園中，他們竟然真的存在。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們金色的毛髮就像太陽一樣熠熠生輝，領頭的那位，他深褐色的瞳孔正平靜地注視著阿勒黛。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛曾經被父親帶著覲見過好幾次國王陛下，也見過許多掛在王宮牆上的歷代阿斯蘭王肖像。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還是頭一回，她忍不住想在那樣的注視下低下自己的頭顱——因為眼前的他們看起來比任何一位國王都要威嚴。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "32_i01_1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 5.0, "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 5.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i01_1", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4, "x": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是坎伯蘭不會輕易低頭。阿勒黛努力把頭抬得很高很高，這才發現，最中間的那位竟然馱著一個人。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一個比她還要稚嫩的孩子，穿著華貴的禮服，慵懶地坐在他宛若鎏金的背上。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他口中銜著一柄劍，一柄......比孩子的身體還要大得多的劍。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個渾厚的聲音在阿勒黛頭頂響了起來。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“阿勒黛·坎伯蘭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "終有一日，你會與維娜再次相逢。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是阿勒黛第一次見到他們，也是最後一次。"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "32_i01_1", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "32_i01_1", "xScaleTo": 0.9, "yScaleTo": 0.9, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後的二十多年裡，她常常夢見這一幕，夢見那些金黃色的威嚴的存在，夢見和他們在一起的女孩——"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到她如獸主所預言的那樣，與那個名為維娜之人重逢。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 3.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g2_dukegarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope02_intro", "key": "$newhope02_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 快看啊，那......那是......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 亞歷山德莉娜殿下！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 快去通報陛下，我們找到殿下了，她此刻就在花園內——", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等等，我沒眼花吧？那不是......失蹤的......", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我們的殿下——她找到了諸王之息！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 天佑維多利亞！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 天佑吾王！", "name": "維多利亞軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_409_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡呼聲瞬間在花園裡爆發。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍人、貴族、僕從......人們擁向花園，看向抱著王權象徵的王女殿下。"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是何等的奇跡啊！"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "熱淚盈滿了人們的眼眶，他們紛紛鼓起掌來。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛小姐......您怎麼會在這裡？", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......艾爾希。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你也看不見他們嗎？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們？您是指什麼？亞歷山德莉娜殿下嗎？", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下只有一個人在啊。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是的，是他們，金色的......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他剛剛還在對我說話。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您之前遇到了什麼事嗎？您的裙子為何這麼髒......您沒事吧？", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......不清楚。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星星......星星落到了樓上的房間裡。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒸汽騎士......甲胄......打倒那些卑鄙之人！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽不懂您說的話。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾爾希，我的頭好暈。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您需要好好休息一下。看看這一切吧，誰的頭腦不是暈的呢？今天發生的事可太多啦。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_manorindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看見了嗎？亞歷山德莉娜殿下抱著失蹤的諸王之息回來啦！", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花園裡的歡呼聲幾乎震破了窗戶和牆壁。人們都不敢相信自己的眼睛。那可是亞歷山德莉娜殿下——她才幾歲？", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“奇跡”，大家都這麼說。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，奇跡，當然是奇跡。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇跡與巧合最大的差別在於，奇跡不會毫無緣由地降臨此時此地。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下的誕辰就快到了......我怎能不把這件神奇的事當成一種美妙的預示呢？", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這麼說。這麼一場自導自演的戲碼，可叫人看得愉快。", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又想起幾位公爵大人是怎麼評價如今的陛下和坎伯蘭公爵......", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到此為止吧，把所有憂慮都拋在腦後。宴會就要開始了。", "name": "貴族男士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的對，就讓我們好好享受眼前的這一切——", "name": "貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176", "name2": "avg_npc_175"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天佑維多利亞！", "name": "貴族男士&貴族女士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_175"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g11_lentinobleroom_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......看來人們都注意到亞歷山德莉娜的冒險之旅了。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下......您早就知道殿下會進入地下空洞？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是一個好機會。我不在王宮裡，恪盡職守的衛兵們就更容易去聊聊天，或者睡個懶覺，從而錯過我們這位地下通道的小小闖入者了。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 原來這都是您的安排。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也有一半是那位大人的自由發揮。他偶爾喜歡在人類面前開一些無傷大雅的小玩笑。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 既然他願意配合，是否意味著他也認為這是不得不做之事？", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......倫蒂尼姆就快入夏了。這天悶得厲害，時不時下大雨。你也正在安排把阿勒黛和夫人提前送出城去吧？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 陛下！我絕對沒有其他心思，我只是......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅伯特，你很愛你的女兒，我也一樣。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會為維多利亞的現在賭上一切，而她們才是維多利亞的未來。萬一我們真的遭遇了失敗......", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不會的，陛下。我會用我的性命確保那最可怕的事情不會發生。", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對我們的前景充滿勇氣和信心。可這並不妨礙我為亞歷山德莉娜規劃了一條小小的後路。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她遲早是維多利亞的王，早些讓她熟悉自己的城市，又有什麼關係呢？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且類似的鬧劇對這個略顯沉悶的下午來說，也不失為一種調劑。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們的精神在壓力之下更需要鼓舞。這就是我們相聚在這裡的意義。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然......我們都有了一些預感。所以才會做這些打算，是吧？", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "低沉的聲音"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，羅伯特。等喝完這一杯茶，我們也該下樓去了。", "name": "激昂的聲音"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g2_dukegarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到音樂聲了。那是爸爸為陛下請來的樂隊吧？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，阿勒黛小姐。宴會快開始了。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們都好高興。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您難道不高興嗎？", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾爾希......這樣的日子會一直持續下去的吧？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和你，還有爸爸，媽媽......是不是永遠不會分開？", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道，阿勒黛小姐。但我相信沒有什麼是一成不變的，就像這花園裡的花一樣。", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#6$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是的，艾爾希，一定有東西不會變！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如說，等我長大，我會成為蒸汽騎士，像那位林奇先生一樣！不，我會比林奇先生還要厲害！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會保護你們，把壞人都趕走。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會像曾曾曾曾祖母一樣，讓坎伯蘭這個名字永遠閃耀。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾爾希，我保證，我會讓你看見的！", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐......", "name": "侍女艾爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不會離開倫蒂尼姆。艾爾希，你也不准離開。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會告訴爸爸——", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是我的家。就像每一位坎伯蘭都做到的那樣，我會繼承它，守護它，直到我的生命終結為止。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#1$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_663_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我發誓。", "name": "阿勒黛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_655_1#9$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}